    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-11-26T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-11-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="328"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d328">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">
                    <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> Papers: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName corresp="#p_RFD1" type="from"
                            >Roosevelt</persName> to Marshal <persName corresp="#p_SIV1" type="to"
                            >Stalin</persName>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d328fn1">Sent by <persName corresp="#p_HK1"
                            >Harriman</persName> to <persName corresp="#p_SSP1">Spalding</persName>
                        at Moscow, via Navy channels, for delivery to <persName corresp="#p_SIV1"
                            >Stalin</persName>.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">operational priority</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Cairo</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-11-26">26 November
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Thank you much for your message of November 23rd informing me of your intention
                    to reach Teheran on the 28th or 29th.<note n="2" xml:id="d328fn2">See <hi
                            rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_385">p. 385</ref>.</note> I
                    expect to reach there on the 27th. It will be good to see you.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Roosevelt</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
